   "source": [
    "## Figure 5-style Sweep for Qwen 1.5B\n",
    "\n",
    "This section reproduces the paper's Figure 5 setup more directly by sweeping activation families and plotting `delta cross-entropy` against sparsity. The default config below is a lighter smoke test. For a closer match to the paper, increase `n_latents` toward `131072` and train for many more steps."
   ]
  },
